# Public, build-time config for the GitHub Pages production build.
# All three values are PUBLIC by design — they ship inside the client bundle:
#   - the Supabase anon key is the public client key (RLS enforces access)
#   - the VAPID public key is meant to be exposed to browsers
# The real .env (used for dev) stays gitignored. NEVER put the service_role key
# or the VAPID private key here — those live only in Supabase secrets.
